# BlackOut ‚Äî orient before you change anything

**Full map:** read `blackout-web/docs/ONBOARDING.md` (product, code geography, data pipeline, APIs,
infra, "where to look"). **Current known bugs:** `blackout-web/docs/api-audit/OPEN-ISSUES.md`.
Canonical repo is `blackout-platform/blackout-web` ‚Äî `BO-AAI/` and any root `blackout-web/` are
**stale, never edit them**.

## Five hard rules (override everything)
1. **No tech-stack disclosure on public surfaces** ‚Äî marketing, in-app copy, API responses, metadata,
   errors must never name providers, DB, host, AI/auth/billing vendors. Say *what*, not *how*.
2. **Every user-visible value is live, correct, and grounded** ‚Äî no hardcoded/mock/fabricated/
   hallucinated numbers. Can't ground it ‚Üí show an honest empty/stale state.
3. **No grey text** ‚Äî `text-grey-*`/`text-zinc-*`/`text-neutral-*` banned on `#040407`; use
   `text-cyan-400`/`text-sky-300`/`text-white`.
4. **Institutional UI bar** ‚Äî Bloomberg/TradingView/Stripe/Linear, not Discord. See
   `DESIGN_BENCHMARK.md` + `institutional-design.mdc`. Use `FreshnessChip` for live state.
5. **Default commit+push to `main`** (Railway auto-deploys); branch only for deploy-risky work.

## The data pipeline (internalize this)
Providers (rate-limited; ONE WebSocket per key via Redis leader election) ‚Üí **writers**
(`ws/*-socket.ts` + `api/cron/*`) ‚Üí **store** (Redis hot snapshots + Postgres durable rows) ‚Üí
**cache-reader APIs** (`api/market/*`, `api/grid/*`) ‚Üí **UI** (`components/*`).

- **Cache-reader rule:** per-user/per-request endpoints MUST read the shared Redis/cron cache, never
  call the upstream provider per request (the flow provider is ~2 req/s cluster-wide). Wire new
  live features to the existing reader; don't add provider calls.
- **GEX is single-sourced** via `getGexPositioning()` / `api/market/gex-positioning` ‚Äî no parallel
  path. Walls come 100% from the options-chain provider.

## Don't-break list
- `src/lib/db.ts` idle-pool error handler (~:113) and `src/lib/make-redis.ts` `family:0`+reconnect
  ‚Äî removing either crashes/ETIMEDOUTs prod.
- `SPX_OPTION_CHAIN_REQUIRED` defaults false (plays open with fallback ticket) ‚Äî don't set it true
  in prod or SPX plays stop opening.
- Real shell is `src/app/(site)/layout.tsx` ‚Äî `PlatformShell.tsx` is DEAD.
- Real route paths are nested: `/api/market/spx/pulse`, `/api/market/flows`,
  `/api/market/nighthawk/edition`. UW key env is `UW_API_KEY` (not `UNUSUAL_WHALES_API_KEY`).
- A cron `.toml` + route does NOT mean the cron runs ‚Äî the Railway service must be provisioned.
- Lockfile desync red-lines every Railway service; fix with `npm install`, not a revert.
- New data routes must be tier-gated via the `require*Api` helpers (`tool-access.ts`).
